data.description: Adorable 3-bedroom ranch in Springfield looking for a new owner. A large living room greets you painted in neutral colors. The kitchen has so much charm with lots of cupboard space and right next to the dining room great for gatherings. The master suite has a half bath. 2 more generous sized bedrooms with large closets. A full bath with a retro feeling completes the 1st floor. Downstairs is large and open that could be turned into a recreation area and a half bath to make it convenient. Partially fenced in backyard with shed. This could be a great starter home or investment property. Updates include Waterproofed (2023), All new Electric (2023), New Plumbing (2023.)Call today to schedule your personal tour.
